[
    {
        "text": "Mechanical engineers know about machines.",
        "startTime": 407,
        "endTime": 3251,
        "slowStartTime": 760,
        "slowEndTime": 5102
    },
    {
        "text": "They design engines, robots and generators.",
        "startTime": 3815,
        "endTime": 6395,
        "slowStartTime": 5872,
        "slowEndTime": 9817
    },
    {
        "text": "But they also design everyday items like kitchen appliances and power tools.",
        "startTime": 6773,
        "endTime": 11161,
        "slowStartTime": 10309,
        "slowEndTime": 16966
    },
    {
        "text": "Whatever the device, if it has moving parts, mechanical engineers were almost certainly involved with its creation.",
        "startTime": 11765,
        "endTime": 17963,
        "slowStartTime": 17797,
        "slowEndTime": 27170
    },
    {
        "text": "That's because this is the broadest of all engineering disciplines.",
        "startTime": 18571,
        "endTime": 21712,
        "slowStartTime": 28007,
        "slowEndTime": 32793
    },
    {
        "text": "Some mechanical engineers, for example, do the research needed to create a product.",
        "startTime": 22425,
        "endTime": 26905,
        "slowStartTime": 33787,
        "slowEndTime": 40582
    },
    {
        "text": "Others design the product itself, while still others design the machines to make the product.",
        "startTime": 27335,
        "endTime": 32481,
        "slowStartTime": 41152,
        "slowEndTime": 48947
    },
    {
        "text": "When an item is highly technical, mechanical engineers may even be involved in selling the product.",
        "startTime": 33035,
        "endTime": 38159,
        "slowStartTime": 49703,
        "slowEndTime": 57464
    },
    {
        "text": "You'll need excellent math and science skills, plus the ability to think analytically...",
        "startTime": 38672,
        "endTime": 43561,
        "slowStartTime": 58158,
        "slowEndTime": 65566
    },
    {
        "text": "...and to deal with abstract ideas.",
        "startTime": 43849,
        "endTime": 45686,
        "slowStartTime": 65924,
        "slowEndTime": 68754
    },
    {
        "text": "A knack for creative problem solving is also helpful.",
        "startTime": 46192,
        "endTime": 48754,
        "slowStartTime": 69438,
        "slowEndTime": 73356
    },
    {
        "text": "The work can be demanding but mechanical engineers often get to see their designs turn into new products or machines,...",
        "startTime": 49632,
        "endTime": 55903,
        "slowStartTime": 74598,
        "slowEndTime": 84080
    },
    {
        "text": "...which can be very satisfying indeed.",
        "startTime": 56270,
        "endTime": 58504,
        "slowStartTime": 84555,
        "slowEndTime": 87981
    }
]